{"tid":2428301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外判商多宗「交樽仔」出現假採樣日期　遲 8 日變即日出結果　違規變合規","createTime":"2021-03-01T12:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T10:24:32.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"21c226d3d7a1e038775a94bce2c056fbf4ccba06","tid":2428301,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:32:20.000Z","msg":"d lab 開始支那化勒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%A4%96%E5%88%A4%E5%95%86%E5%A4%9A%E5%AE%97-%E4%BA%A4%E6%A8%BD%E4%BB%94-%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E5%81%87%E6%8E%A1%E6%A8%A3%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%9F-%E9%81%B2-8-%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%8A%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%A5%E5%87%BA%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C-%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F%E8%AE%8A%E5%90%88%E8%A6%8F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%25A8%25BD%25E4%25BB%2594-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%2581%2587%25E6%258E%25A1%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%259F-%25E9%2581%25B2-8-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%259E%259C-%25E9%2581%2595%25E8%25A6%258F%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%25A6%258F%2F&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt118MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=2695a922\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%25A8%25BD%25E4%25BB%2594-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%2581%2587%25E6%258E%25A1%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%259F-%25E9%2581%25B2-8-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%259E%259C-%25E9%2581%2595%25E8%25A6%258F%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%25A6%258F%2F&h=925c6cb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%A4%96%E5%88%A4%E5%95%86%E5%A4%9A%E5%AE%97-%E4%BA%A4%E6%A8%BD%E4%BB%94-%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E5%81%87%E6%8E%A1%E6%A8%A3%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%9F-%E9%81%B2-8-%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%8A%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%A5%E5%87%BA%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C-%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F%E8%AE%8A%E5%90%88%E8%A6%8F/</a><br />\n<br />\n記者接觸到上月「交樽仔」檢測的 7 名市民，他們交樽後延誤多日才收到陰性結果，不過檢測結果顯示的「樣本採集日期」與事實不符。多於一名市民確認，在樣本包的表格上填寫了採樣日期，與交樽為同一日，因此確定檢測結果所示的採樣日期虛假。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名市民阿偉（化名）2 月 18 日「交樽仔」，遲至本周日（28 日）才收到陰性結果。他在政府電子檢測紀錄網站查閱結果時發現，「樣本採集日期」顯示為 2 月 28 日，亦即外判商發出結果的同一日；根據該結果，他於採樣同日取得陰性結果。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>記者核對全部 7 人提供的「交樽仔」收據日期，以及其檢測結果的採樣日期，發現外判商延誤 1 至 8 日發出結果，但全部個案都出現虛假的採樣日期。在錯誤的日期下，外判商「違規變合規」，由原本延誤多日，變成即日發出結果。</strong>"},{"pid":"11c755e4d60d57e39695e93a081e4360615ce956","tid":2428301,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:32:56.000Z","msg":"支那？"},{"pid":"b5cf6c6adb70e9cc83beb07723c5c240a6f430c6","tid":2428301,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:33:36.000Z","msg":"下世都唔洗旨意零確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f3b8e79c024c968d98fd77f6ee0a8818b12146","tid":2428301,"uid":51790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:33:56.000Z","msg":"造假大國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935d4422b07a8f7641f38d8058f4b5af4c97d9de","tid":2428301,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11c755e4d60d57e39695e93a081e4360615ce956","tid":2428301,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:32:56.000Z","msg":"支那？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"《立場》周一（1 日）向醫管局查詢，是否知悉採樣日期有錯、出錯原因、收到幾多查詢，以及如何跟進等問題，正待回覆。據悉，醫管局現時委聘的處理「交樽仔」檢測的兩間外判商，分別為 Prenetics 和金域，記者今午亦向該兩間公司查詢，同樣正待回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩間lab都係支那"},{"pid":"6339da06715031bdce2d332fc0307035e834f539","tid":2428301,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:37:50.000Z","msg":"本身就中國 點中國化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17daf5c6dfa86cfb30fe2cf694f059358c1ed35e","tid":2428301,"uid":316927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:38:35.000Z","msg":"This is chi na<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b5b67e2c6ca2818bc643c9dbd2694b776ec837","tid":2428301,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:39:12.000Z","msg":"不嬲都有<br />\n有冇人關注啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0889b635144a22c6a835bd6acb9b13c0d112da6","tid":2428301,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6c3a134152c025a4aefa929cb748bd24971ce8","tid":2428301,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:39:51.000Z","msg":"冇中就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a018b937f016b90ed080d6f60f068b46e87bc92","tid":2428301,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那人"},{"pid":"5452125e4d0ea97e3f7090cc81880af2b6f8dd6d","tid":2428301,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:18:36.000Z","msg":"擒日有記者追HA，但HA唔敢答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84081e332ac6252a5b18d289db0dcafdc64fbd25","tid":2428301,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:21:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">做唔切？改日期囉<br />\n比人識穿？唔好出日期囉<br />\n<br />\n再嘈？報狗用黨安法</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外判商「交樽仔」屢現假採樣日期　讀者報料：採樣日期今起「被消失」<br />\n<br />\n報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/386paa1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F386paa1&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt118MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=6bc60850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/386paa1</a><br />\n<br />\n醫管局外判商負責的「交樽仔」（深喉唾液樣本）檢測，本周被揭有多宗電子結果出現虛假採樣日期，醫管局至今未正面回應。《立場》接獲多名讀者投訴指，今日（3 日）在政府 EVT 網站查閱「交樽仔」結果時，發現沒有顯示採樣日期。讀者提供的截圖顯示，最早今日（3 日）早上約 10 時半查閱的電子結果，已沒有顯示採樣日期。<br />\n<br />\n不過，部分人同樣於今早查閱的電子結果上，仍有採樣日期。<br />\n<br />\n記者今午致電政府設立的查詢熱線，職員未能解釋採樣日期消失的原因。《立場》分別向食物及衛生局、衛生署、醫管局及創新及科技局查詢，正待回覆。<br />\n<br />\n《立場》正收集「交樽仔」檢測異常個案，如讀者發現曾經可查詢採樣日期，但今日起無法再在網站查詢採樣日期，歡迎讀者報料。<br />\n<br />\n1. 在政府 EVT 網站（<a href=\"https://www.evt.gov.hk/portal/zh-HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.evt.gov.hk%2Fportal%2Fzh-HK%2F&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt118MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=4d7e98a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.evt.gov.hk/portal/zh-HK/</a>），按「申請檢測紀錄」<br />\n2. 輸入身份證號碼，「樣本瓶編號」一欄輸入交樽仔收據上的「Barcode ID」編號<br />\n3. 取得結果後，如發現「樣本採集日期」出錯，嚴重延誤及其他異常情況，請報料俾《立場》<br />\n<br />\n報料方法：<br />\nTelegram 應用程式：@standnewsreporting<br />\nSignal 應用程式：9458 0060<br />\nProtonMail：standnews@protonmail.com"},{"pid":"b0fd3511a03bc422627bb3f02ec326aa895b48f7","tid":2428301,"uid":241628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:24:32.000Z","msg":"推"}]}